{"tid":1975310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新界東撚入］新城市有個阿伯好努力同大家做文宣！","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T04:59:55.000Z","uid":242889,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"80cdcda546b6259c76c4ca85d9d2020b15e2c43b","tid":1975310,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Px7iQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Px7iQy.png&h=61f58894&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eu9Q031.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEu9Q031.png&h=4c7ac970&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHfMzo6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHfMzo6.jpg&h=bfd3ed6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新城市</strong></span>每晚都有個阿伯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺柱到痴文宣（其實唔sure係咪阿伯痴 手足知可以糾正返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n仲放堆文宣喺中庭俾人睇 用喇叭不停播榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不屈進行曲  同嗌口號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家行過可以同阿伯講聲加油</strong></span><br />\n我見冇乜人理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連阿伯都keep住團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家可唔可以唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保持憤怒</span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n香港獨立雖一出路</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6c2643f5b9e49f52e1e010968d8288e213682c72","tid":1975